== 交通 ==
{{wide image|Rukun Negara Wall at Merdeka MRT station.jpg|1100px|位于'''[[默迪卡站|默迪卡地铁站]]'''上层大堂的浮雕装饰墙。墙上展示了马来西亚的五大《[[国家原则|国家原则]]》，即：信奉上苍、忠于君国、维护宪法、遵从法治、培养德行。}}
[[File:KL_Sentral_MRT_Linkway_5.jpg|thumb]]]]
[[File:SBK_Line_Pasar_Seni_Bench_2.jpg|thumb]]]]
<br />
与大多数其他[[亚洲|亚洲]]城市一样，自行开车是吉隆坡居民的主要通勤选择。作为马来西亚的首都，吉隆坡拥有完善的道路网络，城市的每个部分都与[[高速公路|高速公路]]相连<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dbkl.gov.my/pskl2020/english/transportation/|title=KL20 Transportation|publisher=Kuala Lumpur City Hall|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421195304/http://www.dbkl.gov.my/pskl2020/english/transportation/|url-status=dead}}</ref>。吉隆坡的公共交通涵盖[[公交|公交]]、[[铁路|铁路]]、[[计程车|计程车]]等多种交通方式。尽管联邦政府努力鼓励民众使用公共交通，但吉隆坡的公共交通使用率仍然偏低。根据[[马来西亚交通部|马来西亚交通部]]在2006年的统计指出，吉隆坡仅有16%的人口以公共交通为主要通勤选择<ref name="prasarana">{{cite web|url=http://besonline.rtm.net.my/modules.php?op=modload&name=News&file=article&sid=65671|title=Headline: Percentage usage of public transport to be increased to 40 percent|author=Azlan|publisher=[[马来西亚广播电视台|Radio Televisyen Malaysia]]|date=2006-10-13|access-date=2006-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930190929/http://besonline.rtm.net.my/modules.php?op=modload&name=News&file=article&sid=65671|archive-date=2007-09-30|url-status=dead}}</ref>。然而，随着城市轨道交通网络的扩大，公共交通的使用率在近年来取得显著的增长<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/kl-suburbs-get-25-new-lrt-stations|title=KL, suburbs get 25 new LRT stations|agency=The Star/Asia News Network|work=The Straits Times|date=2016-07-02|access-date=2016-07-03|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702143853/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/kl-suburbs-get-25-new-lrt-stations|url-status=live}}</ref>。吉隆坡的城市轨道交通和公交车由[[马来西亚国家基建公司|马来西亚国家基建公司]]通过其子公司[[快捷通轨道|快捷通轨道]]和[[快捷通巴士|快捷通巴士]]，共同以「[[吉隆坡快捷通|吉隆坡快捷通]]」（RapidKL）的品牌名称运营<ref>{{cite speech|title=Launching of the Cyberjaya Dedicated Transportation System|author=Tan Sri Nor Mohamed Yakcop (Minister of Finance II)|url=http://www.treasury.gov.my/index.php?ch=36&pg=126&ac=2128|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071218184229/http://www.treasury.gov.my/index.php?ch=36&pg=126&ac=2128|url-status=dead|archive-date=2007-12-18|date=2007-09-10|location=Cyberjaya|access-date=2007-12-14}}</ref>。自从马来西亚国家基建公司从Intrakota Komposit私人有限公司接手吉隆坡的公交车运营权后，马来西亚国家基建公司重新规划了整个吉隆坡和巴生谷都市区的巴士网络<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cleanairnet.org/caiasia/1412/article-70087.html|title=Rapid KL to revamp network|publisher=Cleanairnet.org|date=2008-11-14|access-date=2010-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080306062800/http://www.cleanairnet.org/caiasia/1412/article-70087.html|archive-date=2008-03-06|url-status=dead}}</ref>，以增加乘客人数和改善吉隆坡的公共交通系统<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1070248|title=Newly improved bus hub to transform urban transport system|author=Adrian Phung|work=The Sun|date=2014-06-06|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2018-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180406041501/http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1070248|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/metro/community/2015/04/06/ticket-to-clearer-roads-planned-brt-system-will-help-ease-traffic-congestion-on-federal-highway/|title=Planned BRT system will help ease traffic congestion on Federal Highway|author=Sheila Sri Priya|work=The Star|date=2015-04-06|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2018-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180406040906/https://www.thestar.com.my/metro/community/2015/04/06/ticket-to-clearer-roads-planned-brt-system-will-help-ease-traffic-congestion-on-federal-highway/|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2001年，[[吉隆坡中央车站|吉隆坡中央车站]]正式启用，成为整个[[大吉隆坡|大吉隆坡都会区]]的公共交通枢纽中心。

